metadata.name: Unmasked Beauty
metadata.description:
Unmasked Beauty was inspired by the work I've been putting in on my Shades of ADHD and Ai 365 collection (Here on Foundation) where my mission is to allow us to remove our masks, embrace our. vulnerabilities and realize we are all beautiful and have stories to tell. 

Created by Fanzo using MidJourney and edited on the iPad.
